content:
Create Multi-Language Select Elements

Configure Options Manually
In Salesforce, define custom labels and configure translations for them. Use the custom labels to specify options for Select elements in OmniScript Designer.

Populate the Options Programmatically
Use Apex to return a set of translated options according to the language code.
Use a Translate Salesforce Picklist
Create a picklist with translations using Translation Workbench and bind it to a Select element in OmniScript Designer.
title: Creating Multi-Language Select Elements in OmniScript
